37:{"slug":"luxury-brand-launch","title":"Luxury Brand Launch in Asia","category":"Brand Launch","featured":true,"image":"/images/case-luxury.svg","challenge":"A premium fashion brand needed to enter Asian markets with strategy that felt authentic and culturally nuanced, not transplanted from the West.","insight":"Asian luxury consumers value cultural authenticity and founder narratives. They appreciate curated, educational content.","strategy":"We built a campaign around craftsmanship stories - founder interviews, behind-the-scenes production visits, and partnerships with respected creative voices in each market.","execution":"Integrated PR strategy across Shanghai, Seoul, and Tokyo. Creator partnerships with fashion editors and cultural commentators. Weekly editorial content series.","result":"60% above sales targets in Year 1. Strong media coverage. Established brand credibility among affluent creative audiences."}
38:{"slug":"creator-platform-growth","title":"Creator Platform Community Growth","category":"Community Strategy","featured":true,"image":"/images/case-creator.svg","challenge":"A creator platform needed to build community trust and visibility among Gen-Z creators who were skeptical of algorithm-driven tools.","insight":"Creators care about transparency, education, and community not hype. They respect platforms invested in creator empowerment.","strategy":"Creator-first content strategy. Transparent founder communication. Educational guides. Partnerships with respected creators as founding members.","execution":"Weekly updates from founder. Creator spotlight series. Hosted virtual workshops. Early access program for key creators.","result":"150K creator sign-ups in 6 months. 35% weekly active engagement rate. Featured in 5 major creator publications."}
39:{"slug":"dtc-sustainability","title":"DTC Sustainability Positioning","category":"Brand Positioning","featured":false,"image":"/images/case-dtc.svg","challenge":"A sustainable fashion brand competed in a crowded market where every brand claimed to be eco-friendly.","insight":"Consumers detect greenwashing. They are most convinced by concrete practices, founder authenticity, and honest communication.","strategy":"We shifted from benefit-focused messaging to accountability-focused storytelling. Transparent supply chain content. Founder-driven education.","execution":"YouTube sustainability explainers. Supply chain documentation series. Instagram guides on intentional shopping.","result":"3x customer lifetime value increase. Positioned brand as thought leader. Reduced customer acquisition cost by 40%."}
36:["$37","$38","$39"]
